data.description: OOP interface to the Internet Topic Exchange
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
Net::ITE provides an OOP interface for talking to and pinging the
    Internet Topic Exchange servers using (eventually) a variety of
    network transports.

    see also:

    http://www.topicexchange.com
    http://aaronland.info/perl/net/ite/docs.html
